     <div class="bookname"> 
      <h1> 0084 不解风情</h1> 
      <div class="bottem1"> 
       <a href="14680520.html">上一章</a> ← 
       <a href="/files/article/html/42/42336/">章节列表</a> → 
       <a href="14688539.html">下一章</a> 
       <a rel="nofollow" href="javascript:;" onclick="addBookMark(14684532,42336);">加入书签</a> 
      </div> 
      <div class="lm">
       推荐阅读：
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/42/42335/" title="仙劫之三世三殇" target="_blank">仙劫之三世三殇</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/42/42334/" title="全民男神在我家" target="_blank">全民男神在我家</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/42/42333/" title="魔女打脸攻略" target="_blank">魔女打脸攻略</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/42/42332/" title="姑娘好心机" target="_blank">姑娘好心机</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/42/42331/" title="缚手成婚" target="_blank">缚手成婚</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/42/42337/" title="校花的近身狂少" target="_blank">校花的近身狂少</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/42/42338/" title="谁的青春不无悔" target="_blank">谁的青春不无悔</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/42/42339/" title="阴夫：情咒美人" target="_blank">阴夫：情咒美人</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/42/42340/" title="鸟语尸香" target="_blank">鸟语尸香</a>
       <a href="http://www.23txt.com/files/article/html/42/42341/" title="这才叫明星" target="_blank">这才叫明星</a>
